73
00:04:10,016 --> 00:04:12,285
Those are not misunderstandings.

74
00:04:13,519 --> 00:04:14,854
I meant

75
00:04:15,355 --> 00:04:16,856
what I said.

76
00:04:28,742 --> 00:04:30,592
<i>♫ But just want you to hear me ♫</i>

77
00:04:30,592 --> 00:04:32,806
<i>♫ I miss you ♫</i>

78
00:04:32,806 --> 00:04:36,160
<i>♫ Like a burning fire ♫</i>

79
00:04:36,160 --> 00:04:39,808
<i>♫ Breaking taboos and boundaries ♫</i>

80
00:04:39,808 --> 00:04:44,032
<i>♫ Spreading endlessly ♫</i>

81
00:04:44,032 --> 00:04:47,840
<i>♫ Your face and your eyes ♫</i>

82
00:04:47,840 --> 00:04:52,645
<i>♫ Your sadness and your joy ♫</i>

83
00:04:52,645 --> 00:04:56,672
<i>♫ Are all engraved in my heart ♫</i>

84
